## SORTED file format

The SORTED xlsx is the manually curated answer key — the logs your team identified as real issues. Used in the Train model and Evaluate tabs.

Single sheet named `Sheet1`. Four columns, no header row:

| Col | Content |
|-----|---------|
| 0 | PERSONGROUP |
| 1 | Site name |
| 2 | Date |
| 3 | Log text |